snippet.title: MeiQ: Labyrinth of Death Story Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Slumbering deep beneath the four labyrinths of Southern Cross, an unknown entity awaits Estra's arrival. Is this mysterious being friend or foe?

http://ideafintl.com/meiq

Out September 13 in North America and September 16 for Europe on PlayStation®Vita and PlayStation®TV!

GameStop: http://bit.ly/meiqGS
Amazon: http://bit.ly/meiq_amz

Join your robot Guardian and fight through four towers in this dungeon-crawling RPG to restore the world's light! With endless parts customization, elemental affinities, and unique partner-based battles, your experience is as deep as the labyrinths!
